column5: Absolutely brutal. I'm not sure I can stay a Leafs fan for much longer
I'm not a leafs fan "persay".......but I do root for them to be better as I believe they make the league more fun to watch when they are in the mix
Ideally I'd like my Sabres, and the leafs back in the top 5 in the conference. Oh and bring back the nordiques and put all three back into a competitive mode and I'd be one happy hockey fan
I'm not surprised to see a 2-0 or 3-0 in the first period anymore.. I actually kind of expect it, lol!
Never mind the first period.first few minutes.
